<subSubSection pageId="189" pageNumber="467" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="189.[111,1320,293,960]" pageId="189" pageNumber="467">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[113,247,727,760]" pageId="189" pageNumber="467">Breeding.</emphasis>
One female Ravine Hocicudo had signs of reproductive activity in late April/early May; males collected in July or early spring were reproductively inactive.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
